des:
The skill targets devices with Line Atuadores on/off capability.
These devices will control mechanical actuators that will be used in the furniture market (retractable sofa, table, built-in TV, among others).
To find out more about the products:
https://line.ind.br/

To bind to the skill it is necessary:
- Connect to an Amazon Alexa account;
- Look for the Skill "Line SmartHome";
- Link to our Skill "Line SmartHome" (For this you need to log in with the same Amazon Alexa account).

In this way, the user will be able, for example, to open or close the retractable sofa in his house by Alexa voice commands or just with a touch (in the Amazon Alexa application).

To use the skill with any of these devices, you need:
- Possess an intelligent device from Line Atuadores(a retractable sofa, for example);
- Link to the skill with your Amazon Alexa account;
- Enter the same email, linked to the Amazon account, in the device's settings panel (thus, the device only responds to the commands of its respective user);
To do this, just press a button indicated on the board and then a WebServer will be available to connect and configure the information:
- Wifi username and password to be used;
- Device name (which will appear in the Alexa application);
- Email that is linked with the Skill "Line SmartHome".

After configuring the device, just give the command to search for new devices (Discovery).
